I"<p>到 https://mlab.com/ 建立個帳號 , 選 signup 建立 ….</p>

<p><img src="/images/posts/MongoDB/p1.png" /></p>

<p>點選  Master Services Agreement  再 選 Create account</p>

<p><img src="/images/posts/MongoDB/p2.png" /></p>

<p>收到認證信後點選後登入 選  MongoDB Deployments 的 Create now</p>

<p><img src="/images/posts/MongoDB/p3.png" /></p>

<p>選個雲端免費方案試試</p>

<p><img src="/images/posts/MongoDB/p4.png" /></p>

<p>建好了</p>

<p><img src="/images/posts/MongoDB/p5.png" /></p>

<p>建立 user</p>

<p><img src="/images/posts/MongoDB/p6.png" /></p>

<p>建立 collection</p>

<p><img src="/images/posts/MongoDB/p7.png" /></p>

<p>選建立好的 collection</p>

<p><img src="/images/posts/MongoDB/p8.png" /></p>

<p>加一個 document</p>

<p><img src="/images/posts/MongoDB/p9.png" /></p>

<p>抄個 範例  zips.json</p>

<p><img src="/images/posts/MongoDB/p10.png" /></p>

<p>建立幾個</p>

<p><img src="/images/posts/MongoDB/p11.png" /></p>

<p>查個 {“city”: “BEVERLY”} 看看</p>

<p><img src="/images/posts/MongoDB/p12.png" /></p>

<p>下載 robomongo 來遠端管理 mongo db</p>

<p><img src="/images/posts/MongoDB/p13.png" /></p>

<p>看到原本 mlab 的資料庫連接方式</p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>To connect using the mongo shell:

mongo ds1111.mlab.com:4119/test -u &lt;dbuser&gt; -p &lt;dbpassword&gt;
</code></pre></div></div>

